{"tid":661174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"升降機「飛站」開門空蕩蕩　女住客踏空墮槽亡","createTime":"2018-05-11T10:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T12:50:50.000Z","uid":82917,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"634778a45912601ff0a52286de3d2b886c16a535","tid":661174,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ad7e426c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】上水名都巴黎閣發現女屍，下午3時許，有保安發現一名女子倒臥升降機槽底，消防員及救護員接報趕至，證實女事主已死亡。警員在現場檢獲一批疑屬於死者的物品，正在屋苑調查事件。下午5時許，一名男親友抵達地下大堂，了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者(約60歲)居於大廈7樓，上址升降機於中午12時許發生故障，期間懷疑事主在7樓乘搭升降機，惟升降機箱升至其樓層時未有停下，「飛站」繼續上升，導致事主在𨋢門打開後，入𨋢時踏空墮槽底，直至維修工人到場搶修始揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb5daba5b514d3dc02e0b84bfb08f61a9fbe55f","tid":661174,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】上水智昌路9號名都有女子倒斃升降機槽底部，初步懷疑女子意外墮𨋢身亡，涉事升降機已經圍封等候檢查。<br />\n<br />\n　　下午3時，名都巴黎閣有保安發現升降機故障，於是派人檢查，發現一名女子倒臥升降機槽底，於是報警。消防員及救護員到場，證實女事主已死亡。警方正調查事件，初步列作「有人暈倒」案，警員檢走女死者的物品包括銀包、手機。女死者家屬到場協助警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者為該大廈居民，案發前升降機曾傳出巨響，之後就停止運作。<br />\n<br />\n　　現場大廈內有2部升降機，出事的是單數號升降機。女住客梁小姐表示，見到大廈2部升降機其中1部正維修中，表示事發升降機無甚麽意外，但試過有搖晃，定期都有人維修保養。居民賴同學表示，近來經常維修，升降機1個月維修1、2次，運行有雜聲，自己出門搭升降機時則沒有故障，事發後坦言「自己會有小小驚」。他又指，過往升降機機廂曾升高，偏離地面約半個人高。"},{"pid":"e9ba954a08988e361c4d8188708344d995c6acb2","tid":661174,"uid":183383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"CC台都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8866a404362354004be8319753e4a5588dbde744","tid":661174,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ba954a08988e361c4d8188708344d995c6acb2","tid":661174,"uid":183383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"CC台都撈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都有開囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日擺新聞"},{"pid":"26b682429bfb975127f0b8523e4925c69aa2b25d","tid":661174,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"又係公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e3b66ac1c21ca86d6ef9893adfb5755a62e5b9","tid":661174,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"26b682429bfb975127f0b8523e4925c69aa2b25d","tid":661174,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"又係公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aea8696e71bdaa17ead3c1bdd8106635e0b88cb","tid":661174,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"玩住電話入升降機？"},{"pid":"c4ffd9f0f4dc893d8ab0ad42c8725d3071471492","tid":661174,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b682429bfb975127f0b8523e4925c69aa2b25d","tid":661174,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"又係公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"文盲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dbeb7612a9015cd3871b8f273557837b5995e4","tid":661174,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ffd9f0f4dc893d8ab0ad42c8725d3071471492","tid"